  "description": "Visão principal da API Vigilância Participativa (GDS) usando traces no Tempo. Prefixo HTTP global: /v1. Exige Grafana 10.4+ e TraceQL metrics habilitado no Tempo para os painéis de série temporal RED; tabelas TraceQL funcionam sempre.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "# GDS API — observabilidade via Tempo\n\n**Rotas principais (Nest, prefixo `v1`):** `auth`, `users`, `participations`, `contexts`, `forms`, `form-versions`, `reports`, `quiz-submissions`, `track-progress`, `track-cycles`, `tracks`, `content`, `content-quiz`, `locations`, `legal-documents`, `roles`, `tags`, `genders`, `context-managers`, `setup`, `health`.\n\n**Tráfego típico:** leituras em `track-progress` (compliance, ciclos), `reports/points`, `quiz-submissions`, `forms`.\n\n**Variável `service`:** deve bater com `OTEL_SERVICE_NAME` (padrão `gds-backend`).\n\nSe os painéis **RED** não mostrarem dados: em ambiente local, o TraceQL metrics precisa estar ativo no Tempo ([doc](https://grafana.com/docs/tempo/latest/operations/traceql-metrics/)); use as **tabelas** abaixo para validar traces.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "RED — TraceQL metrics (taxa, erros, duração)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisBorderShow": false,
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "axisColorMode": "text",
            "axisLabel": "",
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "opacity",
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false },
            "insertNulls": false,
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "pointSize": 5,
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" },
            "thresholdsStyle": { "mode": "off" }
          },
          "unit": "ops",
          "unitScale": true
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
          "metricsQueryType": "range",
          "query": "{ resource.service.name = \"${service}\" } | rate()",
          "queryType": "traceql",
          "refId": "A",
          "step": "30s",
          "tableType": "traces"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Taxa de spans",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "tempo", "uid": "${DS_TEMPO}" },
